sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as 调用方
    participant Facade as PlugExecuteService<br/>(门面)
    participant Engine as PlugExecutionEngine<br/>(核心引擎)
    participant Mcp as McpWorkflowRunner<br/>(MCP工作流)
    participant Bookmark as PlugBookmarkManager<br/>(书签管理)
    participant Ext as 外部服务<br/>(PDZ/Elsa/MainApi)

    Note over Caller,Ext: === 场景1: MCP 工作流执行 ===

    Caller->>Facade: ExecuteMcpTool(request)
    Facade->>Facade: 构造 PlugExecutionRequest
    Facade->>Engine: StartExecutePlug(request)
    Engine->>Engine: 检测 McpToolType=="Workflow"
    Engine->>Mcp: ExecuteMcpWorkflowFromRequest(request, plugData)
    Mcp->>Ext: PDZManageService.GetByPDZId(UsePDZ)
    Mcp->>Ext: PlugManageService.GetPlugByDefinitionId()
    Mcp->>Ext: MainApiClient.SubmitExecute() → JobPDZ
    Mcp->>Ext: MainApiClient.CreateOrUpdatePDZ(参数填充)
    Mcp->>Ext: ElsaApiClient.ExecuteWorkflowWithExecuteSetting()
    Mcp-->>Engine: ExecuteResultData(JobPDZId, 执行中)
    Engine-->>Facade: ExecuteResultData
    Facade-->>Caller: result string

    Note over Caller,Ext: === 场景2: 插头执行完成 → 结果汇报 → 书签恢复 ===

    Caller->>Facade: ReportExecuteResult(executeReport)
    Facade->>Engine: ReportExecuteResult(executeReport)
    Engine->>Engine: 判断 ExecuteStatus/ExecuteSubStatus 组合
    alt 需要恢复书签
        Engine->>Bookmark: ResumeBookmarkAsync(correlationId, plugId, pdzId, outcomes)
        Bookmark->>Ext: MainApiClient.GetPDZByPDZIdAsync()
        Bookmark->>Ext: pdz.SetActivityOutcome()
        Bookmark->>Ext: MainApiClient.CreateOrUpdatePDZ()
        Bookmark->>Ext: StatusReporter.CompleteActivityContext() [SignalR]
        Engine->>Bookmark: TryAwakenConvergencePlugs(pdzId, correlationId)
        Bookmark->>Ext: MainApiClient.GetPDZByPDZIdAsync()
        Bookmark->>Ext: pdz.GetReadyConvergencePlugIds()
        loop 每个就绪汇聚插头
            Bookmark->>Ext: MainApiClient.CreateOrUpdatePDZ(状态+Outcome)
            Bookmark->>Bookmark: ResumeBookmarkAsync()
        end
    else 动作链继续
        Engine->>Engine: StartExecutePlug(nextRequest)
        Note over Engine: 递归动作链执行
    end

    Note over Caller,Ext: === 场景3: MCP Plugin 独立模式 (临时PDZ) ===

    Caller->>Facade: StartExecutePlug(request)
    Facade->>Engine: StartExecutePlug(request)
    Engine->>Engine: 检测 McpToolType=="Plugin" + Standalone
    Engine->>Ext: PlugManageService.GetPlugByDefinitionId()
    Engine->>Engine: 填充 InputVariables → plug
    Engine->>Engine: 创建临时 PDZ (MCP_Plugin0_xxx)
    Engine->>Ext: PDZManageService.CreatePDZ(tempPDZ)
    Engine->>Ext: PlugExecuteHandlerService.GetExecuteHandler()
    Engine->>Ext: handler.PlugCommonExecute()
    Engine->>Ext: PDZManageService.DeletePDZ(tempPDZId) [finally]
    Engine-->>Facade: ExecuteResultData
    Facade-->>Caller: ExecuteResultData
